        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nFirstly I have applied CheckStyles rules to this file.\nThey were taken from:\n\\onap-root\\oparent\\checkstyle\\src\\main\\resources\\onap-checkstyle\nThis led to change all lines tabs intends to spaces intends.\nIf this is not OK to make such change please let me know.\nOther style errors were also corrected where possible.\n\nSecondly I have corrected all blocker sonar issues:\n-not properly closed streams\n-possible null pointer execption situations\nhttps://sonar.onap.org/code?id=org.openecomp.sdc%3Asdc-main%3A1.2.0-SNAPSHOT&selected=org.openecomp.sdc%3Aasdctool%3A1.2.0-SNAPSHOT%3Asrc%2Fmain%2Fjava%2Forg%2Fopenecomp%2Fsdc%2Fasdctool%2Fimpl%2FArtifactUuidFix.java\n\nThere were additionally some other none blocker issues corrections where possible.",
